# Intuition
Use a sliding window of fixed size `k`, starting from index `0` till index `n-1-k`. Compute the count of vowels within the sliding window at each index, and keep track of the maximum value across all the windows.

# Complexity
- Time complexity: $$O(n)$$
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: $$O(1)$$
